title: Positive Dissatisfaction
itunes:title: Positive Dissatisfaction
description:
Episode 350 - Are you the type of person that constantly keeps pushing yourself? Sometimes having that type of personality can be disheartening, because the closer you get to your goals, the more you raise them which makes them seem further away. In this episode we'll talk about how to push hard towards your goals but also enjoy the journey as well.
